WorkItem.ClosedComment: Unable to reproduce, if this is still an issue, please re-post and attach the affected character files along with any additional steps needed to reproduce the issue
WorkItem.Description:
I chose some gemming templates, and now these templates have disappeared from the list after using Optimize tool.
 
The items in the list on right of character also disappear there's only the equipped item (item level 200 for example) and T9 checked there is only the item 200.
 
I don't think is from the 2.2.24 version because I 've got the same problem with the 2.2.19.
WorkItem.Summary: Problem with gemming templates and item list after Optimize

Comments.Message: Sounds like a filtering issue; you probably filtered a large portion of gear out. Check that everything is enabled in the Filters dropdown.
